Package: pleiodbr
Title: Read pleiodb GWAS Databases from R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gibran", "Hemani", email = "g.hemani@bristol.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Self-contained reader for .pleiodb binary databases of GWAS
    z-scores. Provides PheWAS, GWAS, top-hits, block, and rho queries with
    no Python dependency. Databases are built with the Python pleiodb package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
